  <brief_title>Evaluation of Neuroinflammation in Children With Infantile Spasms</brief_title>
  <official_title>Neuroinflammation in Children With Infantile Spasms Measured With 11C-PK11195 Positron Emission Tomography: Response to ACTH</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Wayne State University</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Wayne State University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to investigate the presence of neuroinflammation in children
      with infantile spasms using 11C-PK11195 positron emission tomography (PK PET) scan, and its
      response to ACTH treatment by repeating the PK PET scan after treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
